Package com.ibm.di.systemqueue.driver

Provides classes for connecting to different JMS password stores.
  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    JMSDriver
    The JMS Driver interface.
    JMSDriverLog  
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ActiveMQ
    The ActiveMQ JMS Driver implementation.
    APIEngineLogger  
    IBMMB
    A MicroBroker JMS Driver responsible for connection to a MicroBroker server and creating both the QueueConnectionFactore and the TopicConnectionFactory.
    IBMMQ
    The Websphere MQ Series JMS Driver implementation.
    JMSDriverFactory
    The JMS Driver Factory is an internal class that is used by components like the JMS Connector and the System Queue to create and return an appropriate JMS Driver object providing access to the desired JMS Provider.
    JMSScriptDriver
    The Script JMS Driver implementation.
    JMSScriptDriver.Ret
    Class used for returning object that holds QueueConnectionFactory, TopicConnectionFactory or error message from the script.
    NullLogger  
    WebsphereESB
    The JMS Client implementation for Enterprise Servcie Bus.
